## How to index List

Vector . .

(v_log <- c(TRUE, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE))
## [1]  TRUE FALSE FALSE  TRUE
(v_int <- 1:4)
## [1] 1 2 3 4
(v_doub <- 1:4 * 1.2)
## [1] 1.2 2.4 3.6 4.8
(v_char <- letters[1:4])
## [1] "a" "b" "c" "d"
#
v_char[c(FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, TRUE)]
## [1] "c" "d"
v_char[v_log]
## [1] "a" "d"
v_doub[2:3]
## [1] 2.4 3.6
v_char[-4]
## [1] "a" "b" "c"
